<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="introduction">‚úçÔ∏è Introduction</h2>
<p>Welcome! This post is a demonstration of how a typical Quarto blog post might look.<br>
It includes headings, inline formatting, R code, a data visualisation, tables, and more.</p>
<p>Quarto allows you to write in markdown, embed live code, and include <strong>beautiful, reproducible outputs</strong> ‚Äî all in one place.</p>
<p>Whether you‚Äôre documenting your research, writing tutorials, or just keeping notes, it gives you the flexibility of code and prose combined.</p>
</section>
